    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali18-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">iḵtu “oṉṟāt tamariṉum” (to.po.41) eṉṉuñ cūttirattil “nāḷatu ciṉmaiyu miḷamaiya 
            tarumaiyun - tāḷāṇ pakkamun takutiyatamaitiyu - miṉmaiya tiḷivu muṭaimaiya tuyarcciyu - maṉpiṉa 
            takalamu makaṟciya tarumaiyum” eṉak kūṟiya eṭṭiṉaiyun talaivaṉ kūṟak kēṭṭa tōḻi avaṟṟai 
            “nikaḻntatu kūṟi nilaiyalun tiṇaiyē” (to.po.44) eṉṉum vitiyāṟ ṟalaivaṟkuk kūṟic 
            celavaḻuṅkuvittatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"/>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali18">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>arumporuḷ vēṭkaiyi ṉuḷḷan turappap</l>
                <l>pirintuṟai cūḻāti yaiya virumpinī</l>
                <l>yeṉṟō ḷeḻutiya toyyilum yāḻaniṉ</l>
                <l>maintuṭai mārpiṟ cuṇaṅku niṉaittukkāṇ</l>
                <l>ceṉṟōr mukappap poruḷuṅ kiṭavā</l>
                <l>toḻintava rellāru muṇṇātuñ cellā</l>
                <l>riḷamaiyuṅ kāmamu mōrāṅkup peṟṟār</l>
                <l>vaḷamai viḻaitakka tuṇṭō vuḷanā</l>
                <l>ḷorōokai tammuṭ ṭaḻīi yorōokai</l>
                <l>yoṉṟaṉkū ṟāṭai yuṭuppavarē yāyiṉu</l>
                <l>moṉṟiṉār vāḻkkaiyē vāḻkkai yaritarō</l>
                <l>ceṉṟa viḷamai taraṟku.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">            While [your] heart is driven by the desire for precious wealth, </l>
<l corresp="2a-c">you would not consider staying away, lord? </l>
<l>See, think of the sandal paste you longingly drew on my shoulder</l>
<l corresp="2d-4">and of the beauty spots on [my] proud chest. </l>
<l corresp="5">Wealth when drawn by those who are gone won’t stay </l>
<l corresp="6">and all those who stay behind cannot eat [it]. </l>
<l corresp="8a-c">Is the desire for prosperity befitting </l>
<l corresp="7">for those who won’t obtain like one [with it] youth and passion? </l>
<l corresp="8d">	The days that are, </l>
<l>Though they embrace to their hearts with one hand</l>
<l corresp="9f">[and] with one hand put on a short dress of one, </l>
<l corresp="11">only the living of those that are one is [worth] living. Difficult, ah, is it </l>
<l corresp="12">to bring [back] youth [once] it is gone. </l>
            </lg>
        </div>
